But I’m sorry but I’m gonna have to give the trailer a 

4.2 / 10 - Trailer

7.8 / 10 - Film - I’m pretty sure a lot hated this because of the trailer itself and not the film, possibly the dabbing gnome must of triggered a few emotional bones for the viewers, I don’t care what a film shows, unless it’s the floss dance -_-
